## Hardware notes

- Input device name match in code: `USB Audio CODEC` (Behringer UCA202 class).
- OLED: I2C bus `1`, address `0x3C`, driver `sh1106` via `luma.oled`.
- If the visualizer shows **NO SIGNAL**, raise the **analog** source level into the RCA line-in (software RMS gate is similar to the BPM script).
